      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my absolute favorite ride and it's looking for a brand new home! This car has been so reliable for me and is still in wonderful shape, ready for all your upcoming adventures. It drives like a dream and has been very well-loved. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
