    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This naturally aspirated power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to deliver 414 hp, peaking at a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable damping rates. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing. The chassis remains remarkably rigid, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback often lost in modern EPS systems. While showing minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the mechanical synchronization and thermal management remain in excellent health.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Well maintained. Service records available.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
