    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really great shape! It runs smoothly, looks sharp, and has plenty of miles left to give. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a solid, well-cared-for vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
