    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the four-piston monoblock calipers provide exceptional bite. Notably, the IMS bearing has been upgraded to a dual-row ceramic unit for long-term reliability, and a recent borescope inspection confirmed clean cylinder walls with no scoring. While the finish shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity are excellent for a driver-focused enthusiast seeking a sorted 911.",
